context: <user> I'm looking for a places to go and see during my upcoming trip to Cambridge. <system> What area of town would you like? <user> I would like to go to the south area please. <system> On the south side, your options are the cinema, entertainment venues, museums, nightclubs, parks, and a theatre. <user> That's a lot of choices, how about nightclubs? Can you get me a couple of phone numbers for good ones? I'm hoping to catch DJ Squalour from Ibiza! <system> The only nightclub in the south is called the place on 22 sidney street. Phone number is 01223324600. Can I help you with anything else? <user> Yes, I would like an expensive hotel with free parking. <system> I have places that fit that description all over town, except in the north. If area is no concern, I recommend the Gonville in the center of town.<user> Is it four star? <system>
